ge roots derived from the resolved library JAR.\\n\\n- `coordinates`: group:artifact:version (single coordinate only)\\n- `agentAllowedPackages`: comma-separated package list, `fromJar`, or `-` for none\\n\\nExamples:\\n   ```console\\n   ./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.3\\n   ./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.3 --agentAllowedPackages=fromJar\\n   ./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.3 --agentAllowedPackages=org.example.app,com.acme.service\\n\\n[93 more lines in file. Use offset=201 to continue.]\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777418897404}}\n309:[recv] {\"type\": \"turn_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"thinking\", \"thinking\": \"\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_081a2cde8c5f7d650169f14290b72881909750867b661e816b\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp8UKRs8vlmZMV2Jon3Yuvfm8xYsQE-Yz51iX5vP09P9FsXNkT89tmhHMY-3Yi_kfcrSWnz2764MxySTgFKLIf3PLAydNuKddV3Hseny-BbYkkSsJO48kZHjZjZBGjePHa09lw62ueEDcm5bL41AATRmWpCs0rg4pLkgq7jn6ZWjPEI4Zu93XhbYbfpLTkzLdcGTPvue_X6mwKkmht2pcYzIdLyygmRMz4vq1wtCf2denDTr-IVXyyH5rh2HvDTUM83d5NRM0KjynyK94UAb9BDUO6qkyY314DdFB6X7sEYRbojBSULHPB5qeKGaLHYpvY8WDTaa7WnVCs8ZyDpFfHRuSY47rxxO33clTcpScjYHwXy1YCKreZO_mC-1ELOq_I0nQ5zoTZd2tWFIS6EIsxC_vbcliMr4Jaroi-qtZ54LxzNDdqVyYFeLPOcVodBeuekcyEUu9lrKA3kmP2oFN6xE9E_3Azfo_MCqFMAl7bpzNOTujRSmkJryS_vhKkFl2DC_PqRTOhf37HV7FtcGJrzlVzGsQMxp7E59TesUpSmETjJsvFg_WCrh2IXrH3qlVt0R5fydJN6kMI7GOdZc0vFdZqXKBhBIsYTNAmeCO2UJ74TgMJBFDJkSaWyPajvXmSNHfK1StXDRYCRcrnG2LvEYXW8t0lVKcJx1_A7EqZSXm1MnXnFwOxoiHLMoFxffvcd8Cvbd4RS0ycYZR69n5PYVRRXQRkZa8kW42GFe4UGnS44jXRdLoA6jEHNgJsP5TLhEKMPchY5qldUfhs885_vo6wrcngp-LABQekP5w5G8nSF6KCEVxpsn-z4MeT2zT1ToU4udTRDF24U2bvPNPgBkVStxtFN3r5pfjovFJA6jhD_rsxlFt3L8xzr5uSSaOPydhOuy541onZGKbH3QVbp0B5VuNXZhN5mJj_nhO5txWdr0Dne4Cqn6HPQZ-RgVdMJ3sg1GX4XLDE3HWceC6cSpUpxsZFKW5w81bnzT9TzGJYUEo=\\\",\\\"summary\